rComments: I took this course online and she is indeed very helpful and responds to all questions you ask online, assignments she requires online were very easy and the mid-term you have to do online is very easy as well; HOWEVER; the final written test was harder than expected, I was very disappointed because I study really hard for it, still found it hard.

Not many instructors would go to the lengths that Else would.  Even when we took this course online, she was there for support.  She really cares about her student's level of understanding.  In return we would have to do the work.  Both midterm and final exams were fair.  No surprises.

Focus on group learning and problem solving in class. No powerpoints and almost no lecture. Really just did a ton of problems in order to prepare us for the midterm and final exam. Very fair midterm and final.
